She not only fixed my lost card issue, taking the time to assure me that the previously issued card could not be used by someone else if found, but also sent me a visa gift card to make up for any trouble I had experienced. Since then I have had nothing but positive interactions with everyone over at Discover. I even recently got sent another small gift card to Starbucks for being a good customer.
